{"tid":615531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五制服團體學中式步操　解放軍教唱《強軍戰歌》","createTime":"2018-04-03T12:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T06:47:37.000Z","uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c235442d404f9722abc44bad093d8637ba1887db","tid":615531,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/204632_5a1b21277b26badfbb403e1568b5b043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F204632_5a1b21277b26badfbb403e1568b5b043.jpg&h=79821f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有教官說：「你們要學中式步操，因為你們是中國人」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報上月報道，有部分青少年制服團體，在復活節期間獲邀參與解放軍駐港部隊的步操訓練班。本報記者收到訓練期間的影片及相片，顯示除了有軍官教授俗稱「鵝步」的中式步操，還有教唱軍歌。<br />\n<br />\n本報收到3段影片，其中兩段顯示有解放軍向各制服團體代表示範中式步操，另一片段則顯示，有疑是軍官帶領學員一起唱解放軍軍歌，歌詞包括：「<span style=\"color: red;\">將士們 聽黨指揮 能打勝仗 作風優良 不懼強敵 敢較量 為祖國決勝疆場</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該軍歌名稱為《強軍戰歌》，2013年由總政宣傳部組織創作，並由印青作曲及王曉嶺作詞，歌詞參考習近平思想及講話，其後再推薦給全軍學唱，<br />\n<br />\n有不願透露姓名的學員向本報表示，解放軍教授步操時顯得避忌，未有向他們灌輸意識形態或要求制服團體轉用中式步操，但向學員強調「你們要學中式步操，因為你們是中國人」。該學員又指，少年領袖團、海事青年團、航空青年團、升旗總會及青少年軍，共五個制服團體派員參與是次訓練。<br />\n<br />\n少年領袖團總參事姜柏松回覆本報指，該團體派出十多人參與訓練班。他指，步操時喊口號及唱歌是解放軍步操文化的一部分，但不清楚軍歌具體內容，要先了解才回應。他又指，未有計劃何時轉用中式步操，「既然解放軍咁熱心教我哋，我哋<span style=\"color: red;\">學多樣嘢亦無乜所謂</span>。」本報亦向其他制服團體查詢，暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180403/s00001/1522749021970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180403%2Fs00001%2F1522749021970&d=FpaXw7UbswzJMEzQO9lqQy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f6099838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180403%2Fs00001%2F1522749021970&h=716c4dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180403/s00001/1522749021970</a><br />\n<br />\nlink內有片"},{"pid":"827425912f95382fe6b54ae16f4224da57973b4e","tid":615531,"uid":30169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"438feed380b05505f95a2f3d2a63eb52455969ca","tid":615531,"uid":10890,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"好波<br />\n三軍一嚟就跪地含撚<br />\n連交通安全隊都有骨氣過你班撚樣呀<br />\n你班垃圾官對唔撚對得住舊時嘅皇家稱號呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e007454ec2c48d2267565ce244bb82388e2b7661","tid":615531,"uid":40628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"咁點解中國人又唔學禮義廉恥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bc10fd2d72f73ea034c0bb705693c217c5ffaf","tid":615531,"uid":33481,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"全民強制學普通話，香港賤民：學多樣嘢亦無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501d0095a5e09c0f75b9b79ae2b7065f8a558ea5","tid":615531,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438feed380b05505f95a2f3d2a63eb52455969ca","tid":615531,"uid":10890,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"好波<br />\n三軍一嚟就跪地含撚<br />\n連交通安全隊都有骨氣過你班撚樣呀<br />\n你班垃圾官對唔撚對得住舊時嘅皇家稱號呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"三軍英式文化咁濃厚梗係要